text: Kuniwo Nakamura (; November 24, 1943 - October 14, 2020)Profile of Kuniwo Nakamura was a Palauan politician. He was the President of Palau from 1993 to 2001. He earlier was Vice President of Palau from 1989 to 1993. Nakamura died on October 14, 2020 at the age of 76.Former president of Palau, Kuniwo Nakamura, dies ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Presidents of Palau
